Notification - Class in com.sonyericsson.extras.liveware.aef.notification
Overview Notification is a part of the Smart Extension API's The Notification engine enables the gathering of event-type data from different sources to one place so that accessory host applications will be able to access this data, instead of getting the data from each individual source.
